Prunella Gee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prunella_Gee 0 Prunella Gee (born Prunella Mary Gee on 17 February 1950) is an English actress, best known for her work in the 1970s and 1980s, and for the role of Doreen Heavey in Coronation Street, a part she first played in 1999. Doreen appeared in 17 episodes before returning as a permanent character in 2002 until 2003. She came back the following year for three episodes, and it would be Gee's last television role.
